title: 02/04/2021 - HOUR 3 - Russell Wilson, Ryan Fitzpatrick
itunes:title: 02/04/2021 - HOUR 3 - Russell Wilson, Ryan Fitzpatrick
description:
In this hour of The Herd with Colin Cowherd, Seattle Seahawks quarterback and Super Bowl champion Russell Wilson joins Colin to describe a few Super Bowl moments. Also, journeyman Miami Dolphins quarterback Ryan Fitzpatrick shares his emotional experience being benched for Tua Tagovailoa after playing winning football for Miami.
